<section class="use-case-problem">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <div class="use-case-content reveal">
      <h2>The Challenge</h2>
      <p>Career decisions are some of the highest-stakes choices we make. They affect your income, your identity, your daily happiness. And yet most of us make them with limited support:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Career coaches charge $200-500/hour</li>
        <li>Friends share perspectives based on their own situations</li>
        <li>You end up making pro/con lists that don't capture the full picture</li>
      </ul>
      <p>The result? Decisions made from fear, not clarity. Jobs accepted for the wrong reasons. Opportunities missed because nobody helped you see them.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

