<section class="use-case-example">
  <div class="container container-narrow">
    <div class="use-case-content reveal">
      <h2>A Typical Conversation</h2>
      <div class="conversation-preview">
        <div class="conversation-bubble conversation-bubble--user">
          <p>I got a job offer that's a 30% raise, but I'd be going back to a bigger company after being at a startup for 3 years.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="conversation-bubble conversation-bubble--ferni">
          <p>That's a significant offer. Before we dive into the details—what's your gut feeling when you imagine saying yes?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="conversation-bubble conversation-bubble--user">
          <p>Honestly? A little relieved about the money, but also sad. Like I'd be giving up on something.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="conversation-bubble conversation-bubble--ferni">
          <p>That tension is worth exploring. What would you be giving up that matters to you? Not the practical stuff—what would you miss about who you get to be at the startup?</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

